document.text:
From: 
To: 
Subject: Epstein indictment 
Date: Mon, 08 Jul 2019 18:55:31 +0000 
Hello, I am a law 
professor. 
I note that the forfeiture is being done under a special Human Trafficking statute. In paragraph 25 of the indictment, you 
refer to 18 USC 1594(c)(1). But you meant 1594(d)(1). 1594(c)(1) does not exist. 
Typos in indictments have disastrous consequences, as I am sure you know. So you might want to correct this. 
EFTA00032974
